Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憶往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帶你弟弟出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啊  迪恩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么了  我當時還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧好薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧你  是我的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總說他會照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了吃蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可以認為我會把任何事看得比你還重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆受傷了  他傷得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在治愈自己的同時治愈薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每次使用能力  就會變得虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經歷了兩道測試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得你還是悠著點比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別好像是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被天使附身的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  他就在后面
