Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:00:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  門是開的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  伙計們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏的時候不許進谷倉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來啊  你們這些二貨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該上床了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  游戲結束了  孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧  10分鐘前就熄燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些小混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我數到十
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們再不出來我要抽你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是鬧著玩的
